longBusinessSummary: OVB Holding AG, through its subsidiaries, provides advisory and brokerage services to private households in Europe. The company engages in the provision of advisory to clients in structuring their finances; and broking various financial products offered by insurance companies, banks, building societies, and other enterprises. OVB Holding AG was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Cologne, Germany.
